{"tid":2517141,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜琪峯預告撐MIRROR演唱會","createTime":"2021-05-05T06:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T07:47:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2b9457f865125f567f7e72994ce45ebef3acc2e6","tid":2517141,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:44:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210505/YETTMGI2JFGKXLKPAGARDVG27A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210505%2FYETTMGI2JFGKXLKPAGARDVG27A%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=c4039cbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210505%2FYETTMGI2JFGKXLKPAGARDVG27A%2F&h=9419f0e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210505/YETTMGI2JFGKXLKPAGARDVG27A/</a><br />\n<br />\n杜琪峯預告撐MIRROR演唱會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VbEX4rR2YH_IwHD8DdHAUBFDzPg=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RCY2QBMS45AF5MG4QFODVGMQRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVbEX4rR2YH_IwHD8DdHAUBFDzPg%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRCY2QBMS45AF5MG4QFODVGMQRQ.jpg&h=ab33939b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■杜琪峯指明天會支持MIRROR的演唱會，更笑言喉嚨痛的Anson Lo因兄弟多，唱少兩句不易被觀眾察覺。<br />\n<br />\n杜琪峯（杜Sir）、鄭欣宜（Joyce）及MIRROR成員盧瀚霆（Anson Lo），昨日到尖沙嘴出席虛擬銀行卡發佈會。做導演超過40年的杜琪峯，今次處男演出拍廣告：「入行40幾年嚟，未試過喺片場咁舒服，導演叫我做乜就做乜，覺得係好體驗，如果有人請會繼續做。」杜Sir表示會與ViuTV合作拍劇集，他鼓勵年輕人不要受目前問題所困：「年輕人係為將來而活。」<br />\n<br />\n杜Sir又表示明天會到MIRROR演唱會捧場， 帶病喉嚨痛的AL說：「目前情況OK，今日會去踩台，工作以外都唔同人講嘢，希望大家唔會以為我寸。」在旁的杜Sir笑指AL兄弟多，唱少一句亦不易察覺。欣宜透露拍攝該廣告前剛做完急性盲腸炎手術，她說：「第一次同AL合作，佢跳舞好落力，我都唔輸得，跳完爆傷口，𠵱家好返。」"},{"pid":"5bc7dff84d19640f76a4e82985648a0f52cda2f7","tid":2517141,"uid":158337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}